taihoa
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number: 2
Definition:<i>Cassytha paniculata</i>, a Northland creeping plant parasitic on (or associated with) the tea-tree: a back-translation from WAIT-A-WHILE


Origin: Maori
